(24, '156 Rhinos killed in last 10 years in Assam', 13, 25, '<p>Poachers in Assam killed a total of 156 rhinos in the past 10 years, including 40 in this year, Minister for Forest and Environment Rakibul Hussain has said.</p><p> For more information, please visit <a href=\"http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-newdelhi/156-rhinos-killed-in-last-10-years-in-assam/article5488044.ece\">http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-newdelhi/156-rhinos-killed-in-last-10-years-in-assam/article5488044.ece</a></p><p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"d8f90718-ed38-4f43-8551-0ca8f70fae22.jpg\" style=\"width: 730px;\"><br></p>', '2019-11-10 06:26:58', NULL, 1, '156-Rhinos-killed-in-last-10-years-in-Assam', '2e5aef1677982fe50fa3d203496b9b5d.jpg');
